  "bodyHtml": "<div class=\"is-container-in\">\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column half\">\n<h3 class=\"big-one-two\"><span style=\"font-size:36px;\">第二場宗翰老師網路直播開講</span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\"></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size:22px;\"></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size:24px;\">競賽資優教育 影片</span><span style=\"font-size:22px;\"></span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\"></span><small></small></h3>\n\n<p class=\"normal-txt\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<div class=\"edit\">\n<div class=\"x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a\">\n<div dir=\"auto\"><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"></span><span style=\"font-size:20px;\">Youtube重播連結:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0UiebnQ01kk&amp;fbclid=IwAR0-hh9Q4IuRtqwT46N7PUM48CiN-IpthMkWlCRCXRQZVMQPFyWXX8KI4Tg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\" role=\"link\" tabindex=\"0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0UiebnQ01kk</a><br />\n就在今晚！<br />\n歡迎<br />\n～關心孩子數學教育 升學的家長<br />\n想成為解題高手的同學～<br />\n準時收看<br />\n第二場 12/1(二）PM 7:00-8:20<br />\n「輕競賽 深度學習」<br />\n宗翰老師談<br />\n1.數學的競爭力-如何學習 如何競賽 如何升學<br />\n2.談輕競賽與AMC的功能與角色<br />\n3.高手的思維：<br />\n如何從一個數學愛好者昇華為奧數選手<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/705229363763085/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/705229363763085/</a></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"column half\">\n<div class=\"embed-responsive embed-responsive-4by3\"><iframe allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/0UiebnQ01kk?rel=0\" width=\"100%\"></iframe></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
